A step‐by‐step sum (grouping in parts) is as follows:

1. First five values (5171.17 + 14264.83 + 8078.26 + 18548.48 + 26867.86) = 72,930.60  
2. Next five (3849.61 + 16166.25 + 11271.83 + 15899.95 + 26851.28) = 74,038.92  
  Subtotal = 72,930.60 + 74,038.92 = 146,969.52  
3. Next three (13111.63 + 18806.62 + 17776.17) = 49,694.42  
  Subtotal = 146,969.52 + 49,694.42 = 196,663.94  
4. Next two (24374.88 + 11125.47) = 35,500.35  
  Subtotal = 196,663.94 + 35,500.35 = 232,164.29  
5. Next three (25108.57 + 15364.34 + 13846.31) = 54,319.22  
  Subtotal = 232,164.29 + 54,319.22 = 286,483.51  
6. Next four (32980.69 + 46025.02 + 5053.76 + 32605.92) = 116,665.39  
  Subtotal = 286,483.51 + 116,665.39 = 403,148.90  
7. Final three (7914.04 + 32705.96 + 22841.68) = 63,461.68  
  Total Administrative Expenses = 403,148.90 + 63,461.68 = 466,610.58

Thus, the final administrative expenses item in the income statement is 466,610.58.
